\end_layout

\end_inset

若正实数 
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

 与 
\begin_inset Formula $q$
\end_inset

 满足 
\begin_inset Formula $1/p+1/q=1$
\end_inset

，则称 
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

 与 
\begin_inset Formula $q$
\end_inset

 互为
\color red
共轭指数 (conjugate exponents)
\color inherit
。特别地，规定 
